## üîó Related OS  

- **IslandResilienceOS** ‚Äì Provides the environmental resilience field within which EcoFreqMeshOS operates.  
- **ND-OS (Natural Denial OS)** ‚Äì Benefits from acoustic blurring and uncertainty generated by EcoFreqMeshOS.  
- **BufferTimeOS** ‚Äì Uses early warnings and uncertainty structures from EcoFreqMeshOS as inputs to buffer-time design.  
- **CivMeshDefenseOS** ‚Äì Shares mesh logic and governance concepts across land‚Äìsea boundary nodes.  
- **Disaster Resilience OS / IR-Defense** ‚Äì Integrates EcoFreqMeshOS data into hazard early warning and information resilience.  

